well there's this new kid i like....im kinda glad that i'm like the only one from my friends who knows him cuase then they won't try to make me talk to him!lol, but thats ok, i need to stop being a goober and get some guts and talk to the guys i like, but it's so hard. It's a lot easier to talk to your guy friends then ur crush.I don't know why, but it's kind of like a law. I wish I could tell this person I like them, but im to scared...i like them alot and they are hell kewl, but i think he's too kewl for me, all the guys i like are usualy too kewl for me...oh well, maybe if he goes to the halloween partty i'll say someting to him...just thinking of him makes me happy!!! gosh, i hate feeling like this, likeing someone alot and you know you can never have them......why must the world run this way??? I can't seem to get him off my damn mind..ug.. ok,ok, i'll shut up now!!!! hehe....we'll frightmare on saturday was hella fun, I went with my friends Jo and Justine and we had a good time. The clowns were scary! even though Jo was asking them to marry her! lmao,ya it was great, there were some hott guys too!!! We'll tired so i'm gonna go! peace!
